Purpose: Implementation guidance and reference patterns.

Scope

Source ingestion patterns (pull vs push)

Normalization and deduping

Feature extraction (pricing history, review sentiment, volatility)

Scoring pipeline patterns (batch + streaming)

Citation/attribution and evidence handling

Confidence and quality scoring

Outputs

Reference pipeline skeleton

MVP build plan

