NS-PIE-012 — STATE

Purpose: Define canonical states for PIE objects.

Scope

Candidate states (discovered/enriched/scored/shortlisted/approved/archived)

Dossier states (draft/reviewed/published/deprecated)

Recommendation states (draft/proposed/approved/rejected/executed)

Data source states (active/degraded/disabled)

